realtimeweb.businesssearch.regular

Interface BusinessSearchListener


  • public interface BusinessSearchListener
    A listener for handling data received about a list of businesses. On success, an instance of a SearchResponse containing all the information about the List of Businesses will be passed to the businessSearchCompleted method, which must be overridden in any implementing classes. On failure, an exception is passed to the businessSearchFailed method, which must also be overridden in any implementing class.

    acbart
